# Time Series Analysis

## Overview
This project explores time-based data to identify patterns, trends, and forecast future values. The goal is to demonstrate the ability to clean temporal data, visualize trends, and apply forecasting methods.

## Objectives
- Prepare and clean time series data
- Identify trend and seasonality
- Build and evaluate forecasting models
- Communicate insights visually

## Tools and Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Statsmodels
- Scikit-learn

## Dataset
The dataset contains observations recorded over time. It includes variables relevant to trend analysis and forecasting.

## Methods
- Data cleaning
- Date/time transformation
- Exploratory time series visualization
- Forecast modeling
- Performance evaluation

## Results
Initial analysis shows temporal patterns that can be used for forecasting and decision-making. Final forecasting outputs and evaluation metrics will be added in a later revision.

